# Luxury Salon Image Generation Prompts

These prompts are designed for high-quality AI image generators (Midjourney, DALL-E 3, Stable Diffusion). They focus on a "Japanese Modern Luxury" aesthetic with a sophisticated, minimalist, and serene atmosphere.

## 1. Hero Background ([hero_bg.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/hero_bg.jpg))
**Concept**: A wide, atmospheric shot that conveys silence and beauty.
**Prompt**:
> Wide angle shot of a high-end Japanese luxury beauty salon interior, modern minimalist design, soft warm lighting, beige and muted gold color palette, spacious, clean, elegant, Zen atmosphere, photorealistic, 8k resolution, cinematic lighting, depth of field, no people.

## 2. Concept Image ([concept.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/concept.jpg))
**Concept**: A symbolic image representing "Philosophy" or "Inner Beauty".
**Prompt**:
> Close up artistic shot of a drop of water on a white orchid petal, soft focus, high key lighting, purity, serenity, spa atmosphere, Japanese aesthetics, macro photography, elegant, sophisticated.

## 3. Gallery Images ([gallery1.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/gallery1.jpg) - [gallery6.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/gallery6.jpg))
These should be a mix of interior details, treatments, and products.

**Gallery 1 (Treatment Room)**:
> Private luxury spa treatment room, dim lighting, comfortable massage bed with high-quality linens, aroma diffuser, warm and cozy atmosphere, japanese modern style, photorealistic.

**Gallery 2 (Reception/Lounge)**:
> Luxury salon reception area, marble counter, modern japanese flower arrangement (ikebana), soft ambient lighting, elegant furniture, welcoming atmosphere.

**Gallery 3 (Product/Oil)**:
> High-end organic beauty oil bottles arranged on a wooden tray, natural light, blurred background, spa products, essential oils, dried flowers, aesthetic composition.

**Gallery 4 (Staff/Hand)**:
> Close up of a therapist's hands massaging a shoulder (or just hands in a welcoming gesture), soft lighting, professional uniform, clean, relaxing, high quality.

**Gallery 5 (Interior Detail)**:
> Architectural detail of a japanese modern wall, wood texture, soft shadow, minimalist design, calm atmosphere, zen garden view through a window.

**Gallery 6 (Relaxation)**:
> A cup of herbal tea on a glass table in a relaxation lounge, soft sunlight, comfortable chair in background, peaceful afternoon, luxury lifestyle.

## 4. Map Placeholder ([map.jpg](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/luxury_salon/images/map.jpg))
**Concept**: A stylized map or an exterior shot to indicate location.
**Prompt**:
> Modern building exterior in Aoyama Tokyo, luxury architecture, glass facade, evening time, warm lights from inside, street view, high elegance, photorealistic. (Or simply use a Google Maps screenshot for the actual site)
